com.simukappu.coherence.distributed.fifo

Class FifoDistributedConsumer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simukappu.coherence.distributed.fifo.FifoDistributedConsumer<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The function argument class and the key class of coherence cache for FIFO distributed processing
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FifoDistributedProcessor<T>, Consumer<T>

    public abstract class FifoDistributedConsumer<T>
extends Object
implements FifoDistributedProcessor<T>, Consumer<T>
    Consumer implementation class to distributed processing as First in, first out.
    This consumer calls putIfAbsent-like method to coherence cache with a key and then call process method only when the entry is first in.
    Author:
    Shota Yamazaki
